{"id":760,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":760,"title":"Isaiah 58","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 58"],[".studySummary",["i","The true law of the fast, with its purposes and attendant blessings, is set forth—The commandment to keep the Sabbath is given."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.1","order":"02.24.058.49792"},["b","1"],"Cry aloud,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"spare"],"not, lift up thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"voice"],"like a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"trumpet"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"shew"],"my people their",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_1e"},"transgression"],", and the house of Jacob their sins."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.2","order":"02.24.058.49793"},["b","2"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Yet"],"they seek me daily, and delight to know my ways, as a nation that did righteousness, and forsook not the ordinance of their God: they ask of me the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"ordinances"],"of justice; they take delight in approaching to God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.3","order":"02.24.058.49794"},["b","3"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Wherefore"],"have we fasted,",["i","say they,"],"and thou seest not?",["i","wherefore"],"have we afflicted our soul, and thou takest no knowledge? Behold, in the day of your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"fast"],"ye find",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"pleasure"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"exact all your labours"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.4","order":"02.24.058.49795"},["b","4"],"Behold, ye fast for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"strife"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"debate"],", and to smite with the fist of wickedness: ye shall not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"fast"],"as",["i","ye do this"],"day, to make your voice to be heard on high."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.5","order":"02.24.058.49796"},["b","5"],"Is it such a fast that I have chosen? a day for a man to afflict his soul?",["i","is it"],"to bow down his head as a bulrush, and to spread sackcloth and ashes",["i","under him?"],"wilt thou call this a fast, and an acceptable day to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.6","order":"02.24.058.49797"},["b","6"],["i","Is"],"not this the fast that I have chosen? to loose the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"bands"],"of wickedness, to undo the heavy burdens, and to let the oppressed go",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"free"],", and that ye break every yoke?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.7","order":"02.24.058.49798"},["b","7"],["i","Is it"],"not to deal thy bread to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"hungry"],", and that thou bring the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"poor"],"that are cast out to thy house? when thou seest the naked, that thou cover him; and that thou hide not thyself from",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"thine own flesh"],"?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.8","order":"02.24.058.49799"},["b","8"],"¶Then shall thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"light"],"break forth as the morning, and thine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"health"],"shall spring forth speedily: and thy righteousness shall go before thee; the glory of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall be thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"rearward"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.9","order":"02.24.058.49800"},["b","9"],"Then shalt thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"call"],", and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall answer; thou shalt cry, and he shall say, Here I",["i","am."],"If thou take away from the midst of thee the yoke, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"putting"],"forth of the finger, and speaking vanity;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.10","order":"02.24.058.49801"},["b","10"],"And",["i","if"],"thou draw out thy soul to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"hungry"],", and satisfy the afflicted soul; then shall thy light",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"rise in obscurity"],", and thy darkness",["i","be"],"as the noonday:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.11","order":"02.24.058.49802"},["b","11"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"guide"],"thee continually, and satisfy thy soul in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"drought"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"make fat"],"thy bones: and thou shalt be like a watered garden, and like a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"spring"],"of water, whose waters fail not."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.12","order":"02.24.058.49803"},["b","12"],"And",["i","they that shall be"],"of thee shall build the old waste places: thou shalt raise up the foundations of many generations; and thou shalt be called, The repairer of the breach, The restorer of paths to dwell in."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.13","order":"02.24.058.49804"},["b","13"],"¶If thou turn away thy foot from the sabbath,",["i","from"],"doing thy pleasure on my holy day; and call the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sabbath"],"a delight, the holy of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", honourable; and shalt honour him, not doing thine own ways, nor finding thine own pleasure, nor speaking",["i","thine own"],"words:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.14","order":"02.24.058.49805"},["b","14"],"Then shalt thou delight thyself in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and I will cause thee to ride upon the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"high places"],"of the earth, and feed thee with the heritage of Jacob thy father: for the mouth of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath spoken",["i","it."]]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.1a","order":"02.24.058.49806"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/34.10"},"D&C 34:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.1b","order":"02.24.058.49808"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-magnifying-callings-within"},"TG Priesthood, Magnifying Callings within"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.1c","order":"02.24.058.49810"},["b","1c"],["span.small","HEB"],"ram’s horn.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/29.1.1-2"},"Alma 29:1 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/33.2"},"D&C 33:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.6"},"42:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.1d","order":"02.24.058.49812"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"TG Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.1e","order":"02.24.058.49814"},["b","1e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transgress"},"TG Transgress"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.2a","order":"02.24.058.49816"},["b","2a"],["span.small","IE"],"They do all the rituals, but lack something yet."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.2b","order":"02.24.058.49818"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ordinance"},"TG Ordinance"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.3a","order":"02.24.058.49820"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.14.13-15"},"Mal. 3:14 (13–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.28"},"Alma 34:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.3b","order":"02.24.058.49822"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fast-fasting"},"TG Fast, Fasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.3c","order":"02.24.058.49824"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pleasure"},"TG Pleasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.3d","order":"02.24.058.49826"},["b","3d"],["span.small","OR"],"inflict travail on others."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.4a","order":"02.24.058.49828"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"TG Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.4b","order":"02.24.058.49830"},["b","4b"],["span.small","IE"],"Fasting without spiritual motivation only engenders discomfort and irritability."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.4c","order":"02.24.058.49832"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.6a","order":"02.24.058.49834"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/1.13"},"2 Ne. 1:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/23.12.12-13"},"Mosiah 23:12 (12–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.29.28-29"},"27:29 (28–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.6b","order":"02.24.058.49836"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/liberty"},"TG Liberty"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.7a","order":"02.24.058.49838"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/almsgiving"},"TG Almsgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.7b","order":"02.24.058.49840"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor"},"TG Poor"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/welfare"},"Welfare"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.7c","order":"02.24.058.49842"},["b","7c"],["span.small","IE"],"thy brother, or relative."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.8a","order":"02.24.058.49844"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-noun"},"TG Light [noun]"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.8b","order":"02.24.058.49846"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/health"},"TG Health"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.8c","order":"02.24.058.49848"},["b","8c"],["span.small","OR"],"rearguard."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.9a","order":"02.24.058.49850"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.7.7-8"},"Matt. 7:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.20.18-21"},"3 Ne. 18:20 (18–21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/8.1"},"D&C 8:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.9b","order":"02.24.058.49852"},["b","9b"],["span.small","IE"],"pointing in a gesture of scorn."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.10a","order":"02.24.058.49854"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.26"},"Mosiah 4:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.10b","order":"02.24.058.49856"},["b","10b"],["span.small","OR"],"shine in the darkness."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.11a","order":"02.24.058.49858"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guidance-divine"},"TG Guidance, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.11b","order":"02.24.058.49860"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/drought"},"TG Drought"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.11c","order":"02.24.058.49862"},["b","11c"],["span.small","HEB"],"strengthen."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.11d","order":"02.24.058.49864"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abundant-life"},"TG Abundant Life"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.13a","order":"02.24.058.49866"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sabbath"},"TG Sabbath"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/58.14a","order":"02.24.058.49868"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.13.7-14"},"Deut. 32:13 (7–14)"],"."]]}
